To Install:

Create a new virtual environment:
python -m venv .venv

Open virtual environment:
source .venv/bin/activate

Run unit tests
flask --app lp test

Create Databases
flask --app lp shell
db.drop_all()
db.create_all()
Role.insert_roles()
Info.insert_default_info()
Category.insert_categories()
Group.insert_default_group()

Run flask --app lp run --debug
